==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water privilege
<hw>Wa"ter priv"i*lege</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>The advantage of using
water as a mechanical power; also, the place where water is, or may be,
so used. See under <er>Privilege</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Waterproof</ent>⟦br⟧
